From: mpDirect <mpDirect@scripto.studio>
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] esp32: Add managed components for mpDirect modules

Add ESP-IDF managed components required by mpDirect:
- joltwallet/littlefs: for modwebfiles.c (esp_vfs_littlefs)
- husarnet/esp_husarnet: for Husarnet VPN module

---
 ports/esp32/main/idf_component.yml | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/ports/esp32/main/idf_component.yml b/ports/esp32/main/idf_component.yml
index cb14ffde6..7d89d955e 100644
--- a/ports/esp32/main/idf_component.yml
+++ b/ports/esp32/main/idf_component.yml
@@ -10,5 +10,9 @@ dependencies:
     rules:
       - if: "target == esp32"
       - if: "idf_version >=5.3"
+  # Required for mpDirect httpserver USER_C_MODULES (modwebfiles.c uses esp_vfs_littlefs)
+  joltwallet/littlefs: "^1.0.0"
+  # Required for mpDirect husarnet VPN module
+  husarnet/esp_husarnet: "^0.0.15"
   idf:
     version: ">=5.2.0"
